 Medical College, Delhi. I did 3 years of senior residency from the same institute and then joined there as Assistant Professor. During my 4 years as Assistant Professor, I was closely involved in undergraduate and post graduate teaching and evaluation, intramural and funded research and published as well as presented several papers in reputed journals and conferences respectively. Subsequently, I worked as Associate Professor, Pediatrics in Chacha Nehru Bal Chikitsalay, a pediatric superspeciality hospital where I was also thesis guide for post graduate students. I also trained in pediatric gastroenterology and headed the gastroenterology division in this reputed pediatric hospital. At present I am working as Associate Professor and Head of the Department at Government Institute of Medical Sciences, Greater Noida, UP.</span></p>\r\n',1,'2018-07-05 18:23:37','2018-07-25 20:38:01',1),(60,27,20,'','Alessandra Drusco','adrusco@gmail.com','6142602573','Department of Cancer Biology and Genetics','Editorial board member','United States','The Ohio State University','1','&nbsp;',1,'2018-07-05 20:02:56','2018-07-07 15:59:15',1),(61,27,20,'1530882968.jpg','Diego Pinheiro Aguiar','diegopaguiar@gmail.com','212154116451',' National Institute of Traumatology and Orthopedics','Editorial board member','Brazil',' National Institute of Traumatology and Orthopedics','2','I am bachelor\'s at Cincias Biolgicas from Catholic University of Santa Ursula (2004), master\'s at Morphology from Federal University of Rio de Janeiro (2008) and doctorate at Genetics from Universit Paris Sud (2012). He is currently pesquisador at National Institute of Traumatology and Orthopedics in Rio de Janeiro, Brazil. Has experience in Cancer biology, focusing on Cancer genetics, acting on the following subjects: molecular pathway of head and bone cancer development',1,'2018-07-06 18:46:07','2018-07-07 15:59:08',1),(62,27,20,'1530970049.png','Dmitry Lvovich Aminin','daminin@piboc.dvo.ru','','Head of Laboratory