raining courses in medical aesthetics, this helps me greatly to develop my nutritional and diabetes collateral. And the nephrology or ultrasound residency, which I am currently following has come as a necessity of niche over-specialization. I am passionate about everything that can bring novelty in diabetes and nutrition, I constantly seek new opportunities for development and research that I can implement in everyday practice.</span></p>\r\n',1,'2018-08-21 18:05:47','2018-08-21 18:05:47',1),(273,33,20,'1534855889.jpg','Paul C. Chikezie','p_chikezie@yahoo.com',' +2348038935327','Department of Biochemistry','Editorial board member','Nigeria','Imo State University','13','<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Dr. Paul C. Chikezie is a professor in the Department of Biochemistry, Imo State University, Owerri, Nigeria.&nbsp;His international experience includes various programs, contributions and participation in different countries for diverse fields of study.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h5><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Research Interest:</span></em></strong></h5>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Biochemistry, Human Biology, biochemical and molecular ecology</span></p>\r\n',1,'2018-08-21 18:21:29','2018-08-21 18:21:29',1),(274,29,20,'1534865923.png','Makhoul Elias','eliemakhoul@hotmail.com','00 961 4 393333 ','Professor','Editorial board member','Belgium','University Libre De Brussels','09','<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Dr. Makhoul Elias. He is working as a faculty in University Libre De Brussels. His research interests and Specializations include Emergency and catastrophe Medicine, Internal Medicine, Gastro-Enterology and Acute medicine. He is a member of the Lebanese and Belgium Gastro-Ent&eacute;rologie society and head of hepato-Biliary and Pancreas division in University Hospital Notre Dame Des Secours&nbsp; Jbeil Lebanon affi