tology</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Forensic odontology</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Geriatric dentistry</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Modern dentistry and hazards related</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Oral and maxillofacial pathology </span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Oral and maxillofacial radiology</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Oral and maxillofacial surgery</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Oral biology</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Oral Implantology</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Oral medicine</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Orthodontics</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Pediatric dentistry</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Periodontology</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Prosthodontics</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Special needs dentistry</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#00b050\">Dentistry and Dental Ailments Journal</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Journal Outline</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Dentistry and Dental Ailments Journal (DDAJ) </strong>is multidisciplinary peer-reviewed dental journal publishing articles in the field of general dentistry and restorative dentistry. It is an open access<span style=\"color:black\"> journal that publishes novel, original achievements in clinical studies in all areas of dentistry, including periodontal diseases, dental implants, oral pathology, as well as oral and maxillofacial surgery.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Scope</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Dentistry and Dental Ailments Journal (DDAJ)<strong> </strong>aims in publishing original scientific research papers including review articles, short communications, case reports, image articles, brief reports, unusual and interesting case presentations etc in the sphere of dental sciences by encouraging dental ailments solution.&nbsp; The journal is dedicated for both eminent, experienced dental dignitaries and upcoming motivated dentists and dental surgical practioners who are passionate to learn, share their knowledge covering the management of dental disease, periodontology, endodontology, operative dentistry, fixed and removable prosthodontics, dental biomaterials science, long-term clinical trials including epidemiology and oral health, technology transfer of new scientific instrumentation or procedures, as well as clinically relevant oral biology and translational research as themes for generating a forum at global stage.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">The journal being an online and free access for its readers tries to provide all its published articles in pdf/html text which are easily downloadable.</span></span></span></p>\r\n','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Coming Soon</p>',1,'2018-06-30 18:02:03','2018-10-12 14:20:31',1),(16,20,'1530383832.jpg','Annals of Medical & Surgical Case Reports','Medical & Surgical Case Reports','Annals of Medical & Surgical Case Reports','Annals-Medical-Surgical-Case-Reports','Annals-Medical-Surgical-Case-Reports','Medical Surgical Case Reports','Medical-Surgical-Case-Reports','<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Coverage Topics</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Manuscripts are highly encouraged to be submitted topics mentioned with:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Case Reports in Neurology</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Case Reports in Dentistry</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Case Reports in Cardiology</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Case Reports in Obstetrics and Gynecology</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Case Reports in Infectious Diseases</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Case Reports in Orthopedics and Rehumatology</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Case Reports in Ophthalmology</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Case Reports in Otolaryngology</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Case Reports in Medicine</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Case Reports in Oncology</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Case Reports in Pathology</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Case Reports in Pediatrics</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Case Reports in Surgery</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Case Reports in Urology</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#00b050\">Annals of Medical &amp; Surgical Case Reports</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Journal Outline</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Annals of Medical &amp; Surgical Case Reports (AMSCR) </strong>is an open access, peer reviewed electronic journal set up to publish articles in all areas of basic medical sciences and clinical specialties. The journal acts as framework for invaluable first-hand source of evidence in medical sciences and a tool most often used in practice to exchange information and generate a more expanded search for evidence through advanced research on diagnosis, treatment effectiveness, causes and outcomes of disease.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Scope</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>AMSCR</strong> aims to encourage medical professionals for the publication of new information by providing a platform for reporting of unique, unusual and rare cases which enhance understanding of disease process, its diagnosis, management and clinico-pathologic correlations in field of medical sciences at an international level.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">The journal acts to be extensive knowledge source for clinical decision-making and bedside-decision oriented research. Therefore, the aim of the Journal is to gather case reports across medical disciplines, thereby integrating interdisciplinary, global medical knowledge.</span></span></p>\r\n','<p>Coming soon</p>',1,'2018-07-01 00:07:12','2018-07-17 20:15:12',1),(17,20,'1530384254.jpg','Annals of Pediatrics and Child Care','Pediatrics','Annals of Pediatrics and Child Care','Annals-Pediatrics-Child-Care','Annals-Pediatrics-Child-Care','Annals-Pediatrics -Child Care','Annals-Pediatrics -Child Care','<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#222222\">Coverage Topics</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:#222222\">Pediatrics Allergy</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:#222222\">Pediatrics Cancer</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:#222222\">Pediatrics Dentistry</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:#222222\">Pediatrics Nutrition</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:#222222\">Pediatrics Obesity</span></span>