-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:#222222\">Pediatric Intensive Care</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:#222222\">Pediatric Nephrology</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:#222222\">Pediatric Neurology</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:#222222\">Pediatric Respirology</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:#222222\">Pediatric Rheumatology</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:#222222\">Pediatric Surgery</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Neonatology </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#00b050\">Annals of Pediatrics and Child Care</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Journal Outline</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Annals of Pediatrics and Child Care (APCC) </strong>an electronic and an international based online journal endorses current advances in pediatric research and serves as a practical outlook for pediatricians, clinicians, physicians, interns, residents, and surgeons involved in pediatric medicine, child care and related health issues.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Scope</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Annals of Pediatrics and Child Care (APCC)</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> is an </span><span style=\"color:#222222\">open access journal </span><span style=\"color:black\">dedicated to the latest </span><span style=\"color:#222222\">streamlined</span><span style=\"color:black\"> advancements </span><span style=\"color:#222222\">yet scientifically rigorous, dissemination of peer-reviewed science related to childhood health and disease </span><span style=\"color:black\">provides a forum for pediatricians who diagnose and treat disorders in infants, children, and adolescents </span><span style=\"color:#222222\">in developed and developing countries.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">This journal provides a platform for scientists and academicians all over the world to promote, share, and discuss various new issues and developments in different areas of pediatrics. All manuscripts must be prepared in English and are subject to a rigorous and fair peer-review process. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"color:#222222\">The publication focuses on sharing clinical, epidemiological and translational science relevant to children&rsquo;s health. In addition to original research, the journal publishes expert editorials and commentaries, clinical case reports, and insightful communications reflecting the latest developments in pediatric medicine. By publishing meritorious articles also permits rapid open access sharing of new information, allowing us to reach the broadest audience in the most expedient fashion.</span><span style=\"color:black\">Generally, accepted papers will appear online within 3 weeks from submission.</span> </span></span></p>\r\n','<p>Coming Soon</p>',1,'2018-07-01 00:14:13','2018-12-17 00:39:50',1),(18,20,'1530384735.jpg','International Journal of Education Advancement','Education','International Journal of Education Advancement','International-Journal-Education-Advancement','International-Journal-Education-Advancement','International-Journal-Education-Advancement','Education','<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Coverage Topics</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Manuscripts are highly encouraged to be submitted topics mentioned with:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Alternative education</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Auto didacticism</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Early childhood education </span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Educational psychology</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Educational philosophy </span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Educational management</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Educational methods and learning</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Educational theories</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Informal learning</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Higher education and Adult education</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Indigenous education</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Open education and Educational technology</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Organizational models and learning environment</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Pedagogy</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Primary Education and programs in different countries </span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Secondary education</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Special education</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Socioeconomic condition and Education </span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Traditional education</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Vocational education and training</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#00b050\">International Journal of Education Advancement</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Journal Outline</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">International Journal of Education Advancement</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"> <strong>(IJEA) </strong>publishes manuscripts that describes or synthesize research of direct relevance towards innovative educational practice methods applied from KG (kindergarten) to PG (Post Graduation) and even higher level. This journal is an open-access, international, double-blind peer-reviewed journal which encourages in promoting excellence through dissemination of high-quality research findings, specialist knowledge, and discussion of professional issues that reflect the diversity of Education and its advancement with emphasizing learning methodologies. The journal publishes a broad range of papers from all branches of education and individual or group learning relating to education, including but not limited to curriculum, elementary and secondary education, higher and adult education, teacher education, the education of special groups, gender and education, applied linguistics or language education, educational and information technology, educational theory, research and methodologies.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Scope</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">International Journal of Education Advancement seeks to bridge and integrate the intellectual, methodological, and substantive diversity of educational scholarship, and to encourage a vigorous dialogue between educational scholars and practitioners to generate a forum of diversified and distinguished intellectuals to publish their research, theoretical statements, philosophical arguments, and critical syntheses of a field of educational inquiry by means of Research articles, Reviews, Brief Reports, Perspectives, Communications, Opinions at an international level through online publications.</span></p>\r\n','<p>Coming Soon</p>',1,'2018-07-01 00:22:14','2018-07-19 23:57:28',1),(19,20,'1530431407.jpg','Advanc