pan></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Piezo electric Sensors</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Optical Biosensors</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Potentiometric Biosensors</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Colorimetric Biosensors</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Nucleic Acid Interactions</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Biosensors Fabrications</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Surface Plasmon Resonance</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Security and Defense</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Microfluidic Devices</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Biosensor interfaces and Membrane Technology</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Biosensors Companies and Market Analysis</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Surface Attachment of the Biological Elements</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#00b050\">Advanced Research in Biosensor and Bioelectronics</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Journal Outline</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Advanced Research in Biosensor and Bioelectronics (ARBB) </strong>is scholarly and multifaceted international online electronic based journal embarks it publication on Biosensors (biomedical analytical devices) and Bioelectronics (Electronics integrated to biological aspects) with advanced exploitation of biological materials and designs in novel diagnostic techniques combating several emerging concerns in biotechnology, nanotechnology, biomedical engineering, immunology, and environmental engineering. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Scope</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#111111\">Advanced Research in Biosensor and Bioelectronics</span></strong><span style=\"color:#111111\"> (ARBB) is an open access journal that covers biological materials and designs in novel diagnostic and electronic devices including sensors, DNA chips, electronic noses, lab-on-a-chip and &mu;-TAS.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">Biosensor is an analytical device that combines biological component with physicochemical detector like cardiac pacemaker, blood glucose meter and magnetic resonance imaging. The field of bioelectronics comprises the subjects of electrical engineering, biology, physics, chemistry and materials science. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">This is a peer-reviewed scientific journal covers high quality manuscripts both relevant and applicable to the broad field of knowledge related to best understanding of the latest advancements in different areas of biosensors and bioelectronics.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\">Our aim is to encourage scientists to publish their experimental and theoretical results in as much detail as possible. There is no restriction on the length of the papers. The full experimental details must be provided so that the results can be reproduced.</span></span></span></p>\r\n','<p>Coming Soon</p>',1,'2018-07-01 13:20:06','2018-10-04 22:19:04',1),(20,20,'1539417959.jpg','Chronicles of Complementary, Alternative & Integrative','Complementary Medicine','Chronicles of Complementary, Alternative & Integrative Medicine','Chronicles-of-Complementary-Alternative-Integrative-Medicine','Chronicles-of-Complementary-Alternative-Integrative-Medicine','Chronicles-of-Complementary-Alternative-Integrative-Medicine','Chronicles-of-Complementary-Alternative-Integrative-Medicine','<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Coverage Topics</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Manuscripts are highly encouraged to be submitted topics mentioned with:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Botanical Medicine</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Acupuncture and Traditional Chinese Medicine</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Chiropractic Medicine</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Mind-Body Medicine</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Herbal medicine</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Nutrition and Dietary Supplements</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Yoga</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif