serif\">Mutation</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Microbial systematics</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Evolutionary microbiology</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Microbial ecology</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Environmental microbiology</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Microbial genetics</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Microbial physiology</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Microbial pathogenesis</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Host-Microbe interaction</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Systems microbiology</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Synthetic microbiology</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Bioinformatics in genetics and microbiology</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Virology</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#00b050\">Current Trends in Genetics and Microbiology</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Journal Outline</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Current Trends in Genetics and Microbiology (CTGM) </strong>is an open access, peer reviewed and scientific journal which integrate two broad aspects of life sciences i.e. genetics and microbiology. The journal as scholarly based publishes high-quality scientific research that presents important findings in genetics and microbiology across a full range of biological science applications.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Scope</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">The journal covers all areas of genetics and evolution, including molecular genetics and molecular evolution. The journal publishes high-quality research articles and reviews on a broad range of microbiology from fundamental studies of the biology of prokaryotic and eukaryotic micro-organisms, to applied microbiology and microbial biotechnology. &nbsp;So it&rsquo;s a unique journal of its kind relating to how genetics and microbiology can co relate to evolutionary aspect of study.</span></p>\r\n','<p>Coming Soon</p>',1,'2018-07-01 13:40:29','2018-07-19 23:39:05',1),(24,20,'1530432960.jpg','Current Updates in Dermatological Problems','Dermatological','Current Updates in Dermatological Problems','Current-Updates-in-Dermatological-Problems','Current-Updates-in-Dermatological-Problems','Current-Updates-in-Dermatological-Problems','Current-Updates-in-Dermatological-Problems','<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Coverage Topics</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Manuscripts are highly encouraged to be submitted topics mentioned with:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Cosmetic dermatology</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,