style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Pharmaceutical drugs and heart</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#00b050\">Insights of Cardiology Open Access</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Journal Outline</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Insights of Cardiology Open Access (ICOA) </strong>is an internationally recognized, scientific and peer-reviewed journal covering a broad spectrum of topics in cardiology and cardiovascular diseases. The journal is dedicated to cardio surgeons, cardiologist, and clinicians&rsquo; researches involved in with ultimate mission in building bridges between technology and clinical research that can be beneficial for patients with cardiovascular disease.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Scope</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">The scope of the journal covers an extensive topic in the field of cardiovascular medicine comprising clinical cardiology, heart failure, prevention and rehabilitation, innovation and technology, interventional cardiology, invasive/non-invasive imaging, device failure, arrhythmology, translational research, quality and outcomes.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">The aim of <em>ICOA</em><em> </em>is to publish articles on topics of current interest in cardiology that will foster increased understanding of the pathogenesis, diagnosis, clinical course, prevention, and treatment of cardiovascular disorders. </span></span></p>\r\n','<p>Coming Soon</p>',1,'2018-07-01 13:55:16','2018-07-19 23:41:44',1),(27,20,'1530434469.jpg','Journal of Biomarker Research and Studies','Biomarker','Journal of Biomarker Research and Studies','Journal-of-Biomarker-Research-and-Studies','Journal-of-Biomarker-Research-and-Studies','Journal-of-Biomarker-Research-and-Studies','Journal-of-Biomarker-Research-and-Studies','<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Coverage Topics</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Bio-indicator </span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Biomarker discovery </span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Biomarkers Biochemistry</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Molecular Biomarkers</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Industrial Biomarkers</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Pharmaceutical Biomarkers</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Forensic Biomarkers</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Genetic Biomarkers</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Phenotypic Markers</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Static Biomarkers</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Microbial Biomarkers</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Geomarkers</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text