is an international fully open access, online journal, covering all areas related to clinical gastroenterology, including studies of the alimentary tract, liver, biliary, pancreas, enteral nutrition and related fields. The journal dedicated to publishing high-quality medical research from all disciplines and therapeutic areas of gastrointestinal sciences.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Journal of Gastroenterology and Digestive Disorders (JGDD) encourages gastroenterologists and hepatologists worldwide to submit manuscripts to the journal describing their original basic or clinical research findings that are of high academic value and which report new diagnostic techniques or summarize their treatment experiences. JGDD also bridges the gap between basic and clinical science by publishing comprehensive reviews and perspectives on important topics such as pancreatitis and liver disease. The journal publishes all research study types, from study protocols to phase I trials to meta-analyses, including small or specialist studies.</p>\r\n','<p>Coming Soon</p>',1,'2018-07-01 18:01:34','2018-10-04 22:23:47',1),(30,20,'1530448583.jpg','Journal of Obstetrics and Gynecological Problems','Obstetrics and Gynecological','Journal-of-Obstetrics-and-Gynecological-Problems','Journal-of-Obstetrics-and-Gynecological-Problems','Journal-of-Obstetrics-and-Gynecological-Problems','Journal-of-Obstetrics-and-Gynecological-Problems','Journal-of-Obstetrics-and-Gynecological-Problems','<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Coverage Topics</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Abdominal Imaging</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Gynaecological Oncology</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Infertility</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-a