ext-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Menopause Symptoms</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Menstrual Cycle</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Obstetrics</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#00b050\">Journal of Obstetrics and Gynecological Problems</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Journal Outline</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Journal of Obstetrics and Gynecological Problems (JOGP)</strong> a peer reviewed, scholarly based international journal intending to encompass its publications for enhancing latest information on full spectrum of Obstetrics and Gynecology with studies on the biology of reproduction, and content which provides insight into the physiology and mechanisms of obstetrical and gynecological diseases with prime objective for women&#39;s health care.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Scope</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Journal of Obstetrics and Gynecological Problems (JOGP)</strong> is an open access, online publishing, medical journal that covers the full spectrum in diagnosis, treatment, prediction and prevention of obstetrical and gynecological disorders.<br />\r\nThe journal publishes original research articles, review articles, and clinical studies related to obstetrics, maternal-fetal medicine, general gynecology, gynecologic oncology, uro-gynecology, reproductive medicine and infertility, reproductive endocrinology, and sexual medicine.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">JOGP is peer-reviewed journals that include original research articles, review papers, opinions, short communications, letter to editors, editorials on a broad range of subjects related to female reproductive system, pregnancy, child birth. The Journal also publishes work on the biology of reproduction, and content which provides insight into the physiology and mechanisms of obstetrical and gynecological diseases.</span></p>\r\n','<p>Coming Soon</p>',1,'2018-07-01 18:06:22','2018-07-25 10:35:04',1),(31,20,'1530450500.jpg','Journal of Sports Science and Physical Therapy','Sports Science and Physical Therapy','Journal of Sports Science and Physical Therapy','Journal-of-Sports-Science-and-Physical-Therapy','Journal-of-Sports-Science-and-Physical-Therapy','Journal-of-Sports-Science-and-Physical-Therapy','Journal-of-Sports-Science-and-Physical-Therapy','<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Coverage Topics</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Sport Medicine </span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Sport and Exercise Physiology </span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Public Health promotion</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Sport and Exercise Biochemistry and Nutrition</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Sport and Exercise Psychology </span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Motor Behaviour </span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Coaching</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Physical Education</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Traditional Sports and Wellbeing</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Biomechanics</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Biokinetics</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Sport Injuries</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Doping Tests</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Sports Communication</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#00b050\">Journal of Sports Science and Physical Therapy</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Journal Outline</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Journal of Sports Science and Physical Therapy (JSSPT) </strong>is a scholarly based electronic international journal framed to blend Sports Science and Physical Therapy with emphasis on current information on developments in the field sport injuries &amp; medicine, physical activity, sport and exercise, biomechanics, kinesiology and combating sports accidental havocs. The journal broadens its framework for orthopaedic surgeons specializing in sports medicine, and to team physicians, athletic trainers, and physical therapists focusing on the causes and effects of injury or disease resulting from or affected by athletic injury for sharing and discussing their latest information and experiences on it.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Scope</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Journal of Sports Science and Physical Therapy (JSSPT) </strong>is an Open Access online journal publishes research articles, reviews, letters in all areas of sports sciences, such as sports medicine and sciences the management of sports injuries; all clinical aspects of exercise, health, and sport, exercise physiology and biophysical investigation of sports performance, sport biomechanics, sports nutrition, sports psychology, and medical and scientific support of the sports coach.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">The emphasis of the Journal is on the human sciences, broadly defined, and applied to physical activity, sport and exercise. Topics covered also include design of analysis systems, sports equipment, research into training, and modelling and predicting performance.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">This is a peer reviewed journal, is an important and reliable source of current information on developments in the sport/exercise/health sciences field.</span></p>\r\n','<p>Coming Soon</p>',1,'2018-07-01 18:34:26','2018-07-25 10:39:19',1),(32,20,'1530450766.jpg','Journal of Urology and Renal Problems','Urology and Renal Problems','Journal-of-Urology-and-Renal-Problems','Journal-of-Urology-and-Renal-Problems','Journal-of-Urology-and-Renal-Problems','Journal-of-Urology-and-Renal-Problems','Journal-of-Urology-and-Renal-Problems','<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Coverage Topics</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Manuscripts are highly encouraged to be submitted topics mentioned with:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><s