g><span style=\"color:#00b050\">Journal of Urology and Renal Problems</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Journal Outline</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Journal of Urology and Renal Problems (JURP) </strong>is an online publishing, open accessible scholarly journal which improvises on practical information that reflects the latest diagnostic and treatment techniques on modern urology and renal problems. The journal publishes articles by peer reviewing procedure relating to adult and pediatric clinical urology as well as to clinical and basic science research in nephrology and renal problems framing a forum physicians and researchers practicing the art of urology worldwide.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Scope</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Journal of Urology and Renal Problems (JURP) brings solid coverage of the clinically relevant content needed to stay at the forefront of the dynamic field of urology and nephrology. This journal presents investigative studies on critical areas of research and practice, survey articles providing short condensations of the best and most important urology literature worldwide, and practice-oriented reports on significant clinical observations. To provide an exceptional source of current and clinically relevant research in the discipline of urology, to reflect the scientific work and progress of our colleagues, and to present the articles in a logical, timely, and concise format that meets the diverse needs of today&rsquo;s urologist and nephrologists articles are published as original articles, reviews, case reports, commentary, communication, letters to editor, surgical techniques report, Image article, Critical case study etc.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">The journal being free access for its readers tries to provide all its published articles in pdf/html text which are easily downloadable.</span></p>\r\n','<p>Coming Soon</p>',1,'2018-07-01 18:42:46','2018-07-20 00:10:01',1),(33,20,'1530451050.jpg','Open Access Journal of Endocrinology Disorders','Endocrinology Disorders','Open-Access-Journal-of-Endocrinology-Disorders','Open-Access-Journal-of-Endocrinology-Disorders','Open-Access-Journal-of-Endocrinology-Disorders','Open-Access-Journal-of-Endocrinology-Disorders','Open-Access-Journal-of-Endocrinology-Disorders','<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Coverage Topics</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Addison&#39;s Disease</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Adrenal Cancer</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Acromegaly</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Adrenal Insufficiency and Addison&#39;s Disease</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Cushing&#39;s Syndrome</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Cystic Fibrosis</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Diabetes mellitus</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Graves&#39; Disease</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Hyperlipidemia</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Hashimoto&#39;s Disease</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Human Growth Hormone and Creutzfeldt-Jakob Disease</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Hyperthyroidism (Overactive Thyro